title: Susquehanna String Band coming to Alfred to promote, play traditional American music (Alfred University)
text: ( Source : Alfred University ) The Susquehanna String Band , a group of three educators/musicians dedicated to the promotion and performance of American traditional music will welcome the public to a night of dance event and an evening concert
